text: Ace High is a 1918 American silent western film directed by Lynn Reynolds and starring Tom Mix, Lloyd Perl and Lewis Sargent.Langman p.2 ==Cast== * Tom Mix as Jean Rivard * Lloyd Perl as Jean Rivard (age 10) * Lewis Sargent as Jean Rivard (age 15) * Kathleen O'Connor as Aneette Dupre * Virginia Lee Corbin as Annette Dupre (child) * Lawrence Peyton as Jack Keefe * Colin Chase as Baptiste Dupre * Jay Morley as Harvey Wright * Pat Chrisman as Louis Cartier ==References== ==Bibliography== * Langman, Larry. A Guide to Silent Westerns.
